title: General Motors Company Q2 2015 Earnings Conference Call
text:
General Motors Company Q2 2015 Earnings Conference Call Thu, Jul 23 2015 
GM will host a conference call for the investment community on Thursday, July 23, 2015 at 10:00 a.m. EDT to discuss and answer questions related to the company's 2015 2nd quarter business results. The format of the call will include a brief introduction followed by a forty minute question and answer session. The call-in numbers are: 888-808-8618 (U.S.) +1-949-484-0645 (International/caller-paid) Conference Call Name: GM Earnings Call 
Please dial in at least 15 minutes in advance to ensure you are connected to the call. 
A live audio webcast of the conference call will be accessible on our investor website in the section. The press release, financial highlights, and presentation slides with notes will be posted in this section at least 2 hours prior to the call. 
A taped replay of the conference call will be available from 1:30 p.m. ET, July 23, 2015 until 11:59 p.m. ET, July 30, 2015. Dial 855-859-2056 (or +1-404-537-3406 for international access) and enter conference ID number 71462726 to access the replay. 
Additionally, a replay of the audio webcast will be available immediately following the call.
